    "sn46.69:0.2": "8. Nirodhavagga ",
    "sn46.69:0.3": "Āhārepaṭikūlasutta ",
    "sn46.69:1.1": "“Āhāre paṭikūlasaññā, bhikkhave …pe…” ",
